## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/taskflow.git
cd taskflow
open index.html
📐 IPO Model Implementation
text
INPUT               PROCESS             OUTPUT
─────────────────────────────────────────────────
User clicks Add     → validateInput()   → Task appears in list
User clicks checkbox → toggleComplete() → Text strikethrough
User clicks star    → toggleImportant() → Star fills yellow
User clicks filter  → setFilter()       → List filters
User clicks theme   → toggleDarkMode()  → Theme changes
User types search   → filterTasks()     → Results update
📊 State Variables
javascript
let tasks = [];           // Task array
let currentFilter = 'all'; // Active filter
let currentPriority = 'medium'; // Default priority
let isDarkMode = false;   // Theme state
✅ Project 3 Checklist
HTML page structure

CSS styling with variables

JavaScript file (separate)

DOM element selection

Multiple event listeners

Functions for logic

const and let usage

State variables

Dynamic content updates

classList.toggle() usage

textContent for safe updates

Clean HTML/CSS/JS separation

Input → Process → Output flow

📱 Responsive Breakpoints
Device	Width	Behavior
Desktop	1024px+	Sidebar visible
Tablet	768px	Collapsible sidebar
Mobile	480px	Full-width, stacked
🔮 Key Functions
javascript
addTask()          // Create new task
deleteTask()       // Remove task
toggleComplete()   // Mark complete/incomplete
toggleImportant()  // Star/unstar task
setFilter()        // Apply category filter
renderAll()        // Update DOM
saveToStorage()    // Persist to localStorage
showToast()        // Display notification
